author: Brande Victorian
title: Happy Birthday Mama Tina, 63 Looks Great On You
text: Most of us don't look forward to growing older, but can we be honest about how Mama Tina makes middle age look so amazing? We're not just talking about how great Tina Knowles looks either, though we'd be remiss if we didn't acknowledge 63 looks great on her, but what's even more attractive and inspiring is her zeal for life, which seems to increase with every passing year. We're not trying to rush anything, but here are 10 moments that mama Tina actually made us excited to grow older. https://www.instagram.com/p/BO2sWsgDsX7/?taken-by=mstinalawson
